title: Gymkata Gymkommentary edition
description:
Before Kurt Thomas started a state-of-the-art gymnastics training facility located inside the Dr. Pepper StarCenter, he did his country a great service. He saved the country from the terror of the Soviet Union by defeating a horde of bearded men and ninjas, and he made a movie about it.

And after Matt Singer and Chris Moreno watched it about 30 times each, they made a commentary track for it.

This first-ever (but probably not last-ever) GYMKOMMENTARY! finds Matt and Chris braving the Parmistanian wilderness, getting lost somewhere in Eastern Europe, and reading excerpts from the greatest book in history written by a gymnast about himself.
